The paper proposes an unsupervised anomaly detection algorithm based on VAE for monitoring various KPIs of web applications. This involves techniques related to machine learning, artificial intelligence, and data analysis, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper involves neural networks and optimization techniques, which are covered by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with practical applications of the proposed algorithm, which are covered by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
